{"tid":1591479,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港航空高層本月起減薪兩成 兼籲員工參與無薪假計劃","createTime":"2019-09-24T07:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T09:29:58.000Z","uid":68738,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b9ac172eedfd8f66d9ec1a9f7fa88c201f96de76","tid":1591479,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:18:04.000Z","msg":"香港航空今日向員工發內部電郵，指為進一步減省營運開支，公司高級管理層已同意9月起減薪兩成，為期4個月；同時呼籲員工參與公司推出的無薪假計劃（No Pay Leave Scheme)。<br />\n<br />\n本報獲得港航人力資源部及行政部的內部電郵，電郵中表示，面對當時旅遊需求相當疲弱，公司已作出一系列減省成本的措施，包括減少運力及航班班次、暫停一切非必要工作項目及招聘等，但仍難以抵銷營運航空公司的巨大開支。為進一步降低人力成本，高級管理層已同意由今年9月起至12月，下調薪金20%。<br />\n<br />\n公司又呼籲香港及內地的地勤員工，參與無薪假計劃，建議助理經理或以下職級員工每月放最少2日無薪假，經理級或以上每月放4日，又歡迎員工可申報多於公司建議的日數。計劃暫定由10月開始，為期3個月。公司將會就機艙服務員推出另一計劃，但電郵中未有提及另一計劃的具體細節。<br />\n<br />\n本報正就新計劃向香港航空查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190924/60079432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190924%2F60079432&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqJBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=875ab867\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190924%2F60079432&h=abeb58ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190924/60079432</a>"},{"pid":"ab335da459e549cff03c151be4587608fe39344e","tid":1591479,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0bROga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0bROga.jpg&h=5e267a10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fefc35e89d13b763f3dc387d3a68090926cb4b7e","tid":1591479,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b446b7eecea58a0761264561a6f298b96528bfe","tid":1591479,"uid":14494,"like"